dct_title_s: Aboriginal land, conservation areas, mineral and petroleum titles, and geology : Western Australia - 2014 / compiled by K.J. Ridge ; cartography by S. Coldicutt; edited by B. Striewski.
dct_description_sm: Geological map of Western Australia showing established and proposed conservation areas, established Aboriginal land, established and proposed marine parks and reserves, established and World Heritage Areas and National Heritage Areas, granted and pending mineral and petroleum titles, National parks, nature reserves and conservation parks in the area and major roads. "Government of Western Australia. Department of Mines and Petroleum." "February 2014". Includes legend and data directory table.
dct_publisher_sm: East Perth, W.A. Geological Survey of Western Australia, 2014.
